<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1918-01-08T08:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1918-01-08T08:00:00-05:00" n="877" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d877">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 861.00/918</note>
                            <head><hi rend="italic">The Minister in Norway</hi> (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">Schmedeman</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                                    State</gloss></hi></head>
                            <opener>
                                <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                            </opener>
                            <opener>
                                <dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Christiania</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1918-01-08T14:00:00+01:00"><hi rend="italic">January 8, 1918, 2 p.m.</hi></date>
                                    <lb/> [<hi rend="italic">Received 5.52 p.m.</hi>]</dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>451. A Finnish commission is to arrive here to-day for the purpose of
                                requesting recognition by the Norwegian Government of Finnish
                                independence. Minister for Foreign Affairs informed me <pb facs="0831" n="741" xml:id="pg_741"/> this morning that
                                independence of Finland would undoubtedly be recognized by
                                Norway.</p>
                            <p>The press reports that one or more members of the commission will
                                proceed from here to the United States.</p>
                            <closer>
                                <signed><persName><hi rend="smallcaps">Schmedeman</hi></persName></signed>
                            </closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>